---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../components/Disclaimer.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About Antonio Rodríguez Martínez"
	description="Systems builder. Technical program manager. Father. I write, build, and create."
>
	<!-- Hero Image - Full width, properly contained -->
	<div class="mb-8 md:mb-12 animate-fade-up">
		<img 
			src="/images/mia-y-yo-anime.avif" 
			alt="Antonio Rodríguez Martínez and his daughter Mia in anime style" 
			class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
			loading="eager"
		/>
	</div>

	<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 prose prose-lg max-w-none">
		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-1">
			I build systems — digital, emotional, spiritual, and physical.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-2">
			I'm a technical program manager, software architect, and developer with over a decade of experience building scalable products. I've founded companies, led teams, and shipped software used by millions. Now I split my time between building tools and raising my kids.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-3">
			I'm also a father, artist, martial artist, mentor, and the founder of <strong>Strong Hands, Soft Heart</strong> — a brand devoted to practical strength, emotional depth, and sacred self-reliance.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-4">
			This blog documents raw reflections on:
		</p>

		<ul class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-5">
			<li><strong>Art & Expression</strong> 🎵 — creative soul, aesthetic power, truth-telling</li>
			<li><strong>Culture</strong> 🌍 — social norms, collective behavior, and cultural critique</li>
			<li><strong>DIY & Creation</strong> 🛠️ — physical builds, handmade goods, crafting</li>
			<li><strong>Integration & Growth</strong> 🧘🏽‍♂️ — inner mastery, parenting, masculine leadership</li>
			<li><strong>Learning Projects</strong> 📚 — documentation of mastery in progress</li>
			<li><strong>Metaspace</strong> 🌀 — reflections on the journey itself</li>
			<li><strong>Parenting</strong> 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 — raising resilient children, family dynamics, and personal growth</li>
			<li><strong>Politics</strong> ⚖️ — power dynamics, social structures, and collective healing</li>
			<li><strong>Psychology</strong> 🧠 — human behavior, social dynamics, and mental processes</li>
			<li><strong>Systems & Strategy</strong> 💻 — technical systems, organizational design, and strategic thinking</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-6">👇 Links</h2>

		<ul class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-7">
			<li>🛠 <a href="https://builds.software" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Builds.software</a> — my technical portfolio</li>
			<li>💜 <a href="https://stronghandssoftheart.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Strong Hands, Soft Heart</a> — my brand</li>
			<li>🐙 <a href="https://github.com/antoniwan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a> — open source & code</li>
			<li>🌀 <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/antoniwan.online" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BlueSky</a> — my social brain</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8">
			For collaboration or questions, get in touch!
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8">
			I've also built some <strong>meta-tools</strong> to understand my own creative patterns. The <a href="/brain-science" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">🧠 Brain Science</a> section analyzes my writing cadence, topic evolution, and intellectual journey through data visualization. The <a href="/tag-management" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">🏷️ Tag Management</a> page provides insights into how I organize and categorize my thoughts — a window into my mental filing system. I've also created <a href="/api/" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">💬 API Documentation</a> with development tools including a curated collection of Stoic philosophy quotes for personal use and blog integration.
		</p>

		<div class="card-alt p-6 border-l-4 border-[rgb(var(--color-primary))] animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8" role="complementary" aria-label="Disclaimer">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
				<span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">🌟</span>
				<span class="font-semibold">Sacred Disclaimer</span>
			</div>
			<p class="text-body-muted m-0">The wisdom, practices, and digital alchemy shared here flow from personal experience and creative exploration. None of this constitutes medical, legal, psychological, or professional advice. Please consult qualified professionals for such guidance.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
